{"title":"拓扑序计数","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":125,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-1304","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>求一颗有根树/树形图的拓扑序个数.</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>第一行一个n和一个素数P,表示这颗树有n个节点,要求拓扑序个数modP之后的结果.</p>\n<p>接下来n-1行,每行有两个数字x和y,表示x是y的父亲.</p>\n<p>保证1&lt;=n&lt;=1500000, n&lt;P&lt;2^31,P为质数.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>一行一个数字,为该树形图拓扑序个数modP的结果.</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>样例1<br>4 100000007<br>1 2<br>1 3<br>2 4<br><br>样例2<br>6 100000007<br>1 2<br>2 3<br>1 4<br>3 5<br>5 6</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>样例1<br>3<br><br>样例2<br>5</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>每个非根节点的儿子个数平均较多,数据量较大,建议c/c++选手才用scanf的读入方式</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}